com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang

Class PointSample

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.PointSample

  • public final class PointSample
extends Object
    Represents an evaluation record used during an optimization search. We track both a record of the network's state, and a record of the gradient evaluated at that point.
